Text:
Opened VST V-Station in FL 9, it asked for a name plus the regsitry number.

I enter the number and my alias, FL Locks up non responsive. 

Please advise.

Stop bullshiting, works perfect! Just change installation folder to Image-Line/Fl Studio 10/Plugins /Vst

And there is no trojan!

This 1.6 installer is the ONLY install that will work on Win7 properly & easily. Do not mess with other versions.

Thanks to uploader.
